<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>user_registration_request</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Auto approve user registration requests</name><order>150</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {

	createUserFromRegistration();
function createUserFromRegistration() {
   //create user record and notify user
   var usr = new GlideRecord("sys_user");
   usr.first_name = current.first_name;
   usr.last_name = current.last_name;
   usr.email = current.email;
   usr.user_name = current.email;
   usr.u_applicant = 'true';
   usr.roles = 'x_210319_ats.jobs_user';
   
   //generate random password
   var newpw = "";
   var availablechars = "23456789ABCDEFGHJKLMNPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghjkmnpqrstuvwxyz";
   for (var x = 0; x < 8; x++) {
      randomNumber = Math.floor(Math.random() * availablechars.length);
      newpw += availablechars[randomNumber];
   }
   usr.user_password.setDisplayValue(newpw);
   usr.password_needs_reset = true;
   var userid = usr.insert();
   
   current.state = "processed";
   current.user = userid;
   current.update();
   
   gs.eventQueue("user_registration_processed", usr, usr.email, newpw);
   gs.addInfoMessage(gs.getMessage("User account created, user will be notified."));
}

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-03-27 22:22:38</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>5b6b6eee370513009af1097973990eae</sys_id><sys_mod_count>3</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Auto approve user registration requests</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_5b6b6eee370513009af1097973990eae</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-03-27 23:48:20</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=5b6b6eee370513009af1097973990eae"/></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access/><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>true</client_callable><collection>user_registration_request</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Auto Process User Registration</name><order>200</order><priority/><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[/*
 * Create a user account from a user registration if we have auto process enabled. Creates account and notifies user.
 * Service-now.com
 */

if (gs.getProperty("com.snc.user_registration_auto_process") == "true") {
createUserFromRegistration();
}
else {
   gs.addInfoMessage("Your request has been submitted and is pending review. You will receive an email when your request is processed.");
}



function createUserFromRegistration() {
   //create user record and notify user
   var usr = new GlideRecord("sys_user");
   usr.first_name = current.first_name;
   usr.last_name = current.last_name;
   usr.email = current.email;
   usr.user_name = current.email;
   
   //generate random password
   var newpw = "";
   var availablechars = "23456789ABCDEFGHJKLMNPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghjkmnpqrstuvwxyz";
   for (var x = 0; x < 8; x++) {
      randomNumber = Math.floor(Math.random() * availablechars.length);
      newpw += availablechars[randomNumber];
   }
   usr.user_password.setDisplayValue(newpw);
   usr.password_needs_reset = true;
   var userid = usr.insert();
   
   current.state = "processed";
   current.user = userid;
   current.update();
   
   gs.eventQueue("user_registration_processed", usr, usr.email, newpw);
   gs.addInfoMessage(gs.getMessage("Your request has been processed. You will receive an email shortly with your user name and temporary password."));
   gs.setRedirect("welcome.do");
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>bruggeri</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2010-04-16 01:07:21</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>0427deda0a0a3c7401ac521ccda507f9</sys_id><sys_mod_count>16</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Auto Process User Registration</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="User Registration Request" source="com.snc.user_registration">e84f1ea2370513009af1097973990ea4</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_0427deda0a0a3c7401ac521ccda507f9</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-03-27 22:09:31</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=0427deda0a0a3c7401ac521ccda507f9"/></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sysevent_script_action"><sysevent_script_action action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>false</active><condition_script/><description/><event_name>login.failed</event_name><name>SNC User Lockout Check with Auto Unlock</name><order>100</order><script><![CDATA[//
// Check to see if the user has failed to login too many times
// when the limit is reached, lock the user out of the system.
// Also create a trigger to unlock the user after 'N' minutes.
//

lockoutOnFailedLogin();

function lockoutOnFailedLogin() {
	var maxUnlockAttempts = gs.getProperty("glide.user.max_unlock_attempts", 5);
	var gr = new GlideRecord("sys_user");
	if (gr.get("user_name", event.parm1.toString())) {
		if (gr.failed_attempts > maxUnlockAttempts)
			return;

		gr.failed_attempts += 1;
		if (gr.failed_attempts > maxUnlockAttempts) {
			gr.locked_out = true;
			gr.update();
			gs.log("User " + event.parm1 + " locked out due to too many invalid login attempts");
			triggerUnlock(gr.sys_id);
		} else {
			gr.update();       
		}
	}
}

function triggerUnlock(userSysID) {
	var unlockIn = gs.getProperty("glide.user.unlock_timeout_in_mins", 15);
	var trigger = new GlideRecord("sys_trigger");
	trigger.name = "Unlock the user after "+ unlockIn + " mins";
	trigger.next_action = getTriggerTime(unlockIn);
	trigger.job_id.setDisplayValue('RunScriptJob');
	trigger.script = getTriggerScript(userSysID);
	trigger.document = 'sys_user';
	trigger.document_key = userSysID;
	trigger.state = 0;
	trigger.trigger_type = 0;
	trigger.insert();
}

function getTriggerScript(userSysID) {
	var ret = ""
	+ "var gr = new GlideRecord('sys_user');\n"
	+ "gr.addQuery('sys_id', '" +userSysID+ "');\n"
	+ "gr.addQuery('locked_out', true);\n"
	+ "gr.query();\n"
	+ "if (gr.next()) {\n"
		+ "gr.locked_out = false;\n"
		+ "gr.failed_attempts = 0;\n"
		+ "gr.update();\n"
		+ "gs.log('Auto-unlocking user '+gr.name);\n"
	+ "} else {\n"
		+ "gs.log('Unable to auto-unlock user with sys_id: "+userSysID+"');\n"
	+ "}";
	return ret;
}

function getTriggerTime(minutesToAdd) {
	var checkTime = new GlideDateTime(/*now*/);
